{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3922c","heading":"Integration of foreign economic policy","label":"3922c Integration of foreign economic policy","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/ch52/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs3922c","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Department of State Authorities Act, Fiscal Year 2017, and not as part of the Foreign Service Act of 1980 which comprises this chapter.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","DefinitionsFor definitions of “Secretary”, “Department”, and “Foreign Service” as used in this section, see , set out as a note under .section 2 of Pub. L. 114–323section 2651 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs3922c%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs3922c%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"foreign economic policy priorities for each regional bureau, including for individual countries, as appropriate; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t22/s3922c/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft22%2Fs3922c%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"policies and guidanc